---
const photos = [
  { src: '/photos/lx470/exterior-front-3q.jpg', alt: '1998 Lexus LX470, front three-quarter view' },
  { src: '/photos/lx470/exterior-side.jpg', alt: 'Driver side profile' },
  { src: '/photos/lx470/exterior-rear-3q.jpg', alt: 'Rear three-quarter view' },
  { src: '/photos/lx470/exterior-rear.jpg', alt: 'Straight rear view' },
  { src: '/photos/lx470/exterior-front.jpg', alt: 'Straight front view' },
  { src: '/photos/lx470/interior-front.jpg', alt: 'Front seats and dashboard' },
  { src: '/photos/lx470/interior-dash.jpg', alt: 'Dashboard and console detail' },
  { src: '/photos/lx470/interior-doors-open.jpg', alt: 'Doors open, interior condition' },
  { src: '/photos/lx470/cargo.jpg', alt: 'Cargo area, seats up' },
  { src: '/photos/lx470/cargo-open.jpg', alt: 'Rear tailgate and cargo door open' },
];
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow" />
    <title>1998 Lexus LX470 — For Sale</title>
    <meta name="description" content="1998 Lexus LX470 for sale. Lifetime West Coast car, bone dry, no rust, recently serviced." />
    <style>
      :root {
        --ink: #1c1c1a;
        --ink-soft: #5a5a54;
        --line: #e3e0d8;
        --bg: #faf9f6;
        --accent: #6b3d2e;
      }
      * { box-sizing: border-box; }
      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        color: var(--ink);
        background: var(--bg);
        line-height: 1.55;
      }
      .wrap { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px; }
      header.page-head {
        padding: 36px 0 24px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
      }
      header.page-head .kicker {
        font-size: 13px;
        letter-spacing: 0.06em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--ink-soft);
        margin-bottom: 6px;
      }
      h1 { font-size: 32px; margin: 0 0 8px; }
      .price-row {
        display: flex;
        align-items: baseline;
        gap: 14px;
        margin-top: 10px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }
      .price {
        font-size: 28px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--accent);
      }
      .odo { color: var(--ink-soft); font-size: 15px; }
      .gallery {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
        gap: 10px;
        margin: 28px 0;
      }
      .gallery img {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        object-fit: cover;
        border-radius: 8px;
        display: block;
        aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
      }
      .gallery a:first-child {
        grid-column: 1 / -1;
      }
      .gallery a:first-child img {
        aspect-ratio: 16 / 10;
      }
      section { padding: 24px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); }
      section:last-of-type { border-bottom: none; }
      h2 { font-size: 20px; margin: 0 0 14px; }
      ul.spec-list {
        list-style: none;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 10px 24px;
      }
      ul.spec-list li {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 12px;
        padding: 8px 0;
        border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--line);
        font-size: 15px;
      }
      ul.spec-list li b { text-align: right; }
      ul.checklist { padding-left: 20px; margin: 0; }
      ul.checklist li { margin-bottom: 8px; }
      .callout {
        background: #f3efe6;
        border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
        padding: 14px 16px;
        border-radius: 4px;
        font-size: 14.5px;
        margin-top: 16px;
      }
      .contact {
        background: var(--ink);
        color: #fff;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 32px 20px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        margin: 28px 0;
      }
      .contact a {
        color: #fff;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 18px;
      }
      footer {
        text-align: center;
        color: var(--ink-soft);
        font-size: 12.5px;
        padding: 24px 20px 40px;
      }
      @media (max-width: 560px) {
        .gallery { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
        ul.spec-list { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        h1 { font-size: 26px; }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="wrap">
      <header class="page-head">
        <div class="kicker">For Sale · Private Party</div>
        <h1>1998 Lexus LX470</h1>
        <div class="price-row">
          <span class="odo">Bone dry, no rust · lifetime West Coast car</span>
        </div>
      </header>

      <section>
        <div class="gallery">
          {photos.map((p) => (
            <a href={p.src} target="_blank" rel="noopener">
              <img src={p.src} alt={p.alt} loading="lazy" />
            </a>
          ))}
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>The short version</h2>
        <p>
          A well-kept 1998 LX470 — Toyota Land Cruiser mechanicals under Lexus trim, the version most people
          quietly agree they should have bought. Corporate car early in its life, then owned and driven on the
          West Coast since. Bone dry, no rust. Just detailed and ready for its next set of adventures.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Condition & history</h2>
        <ul class="checklist">
          <li>Purchased from Sacramento, CA — corporate car prior to our ownership</li>
          <li>Lifetime West Coast car, dry climate throughout — no rust, no rot</li>
          <li>Recent oil change</li>
          <li>Recent transmission service</li>
          <li>All receipts on hand from every owner</li>
          <li>Everything works as it should, with one exception: the automatic passenger-side mirror retractor doesn't operate (manual adjustment fine)</li>
          <li>Just detailed, inside and out</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="callout">
          <b>Documentation:</b> full CARFAX and the complete service file are available to serious buyers —
          documented accident-free ownership history aside from one minor, reported incident, and a long
          service record. Ask and we'll send it over.
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Specs</h2>
        <ul class="spec-list">
          <li>Year <b>1998</b></li>
          <li>Model <b>LX470</b></li>
          <li>Engine <b>4.7L V8</b></li>
          <li>Drivetrain <b>Full-time AWD</b></li>
          <li>Body <b>4-door wagon / SUV</b></li>
          <li>Location <b>Pacific Northwest</b></li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <div class="contact">
        <p style="margin:0 0 10px;font-size:15px;">Interested? Reach out directly.</p>
        <a href="mailto:rustymetty@gmail.com">rustymetty@gmail.com</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <footer>
      This is a standalone listing page and is not part of 356workshop.com's restoration content.
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
